node.text:
I had so much fun with my dance family this past weekend competing and taking amazing dance classes from the talented teachers at @velocitydanceconvention! I’m so very thankful for my MVA scholarship and I’m honored that Velocity chose me as the MVA winner in the mini room.  I’m also so grateful to have received a diamond & first overall for my solo choreographed by @thealexalba 🙌🏻 I can’t wait to dance in the nationals finale show (choreographed by @wbezz) with my talented, fun Pave friends who also received scholarships.  Congrats  friends!  @paveschoolofthearts
Song: Rescue by @lauren_daigle

node.text:
Getting called out with the older girls was so much fun! Loved my time at @autumnmiller @markmeismer & @toddflanagan intensive🙌🏻 Especially loved dancing next to @kinleyfullout who is a girl I REALLY look up to as a dancer. All of these dancers are amazing and pushed me to work extra hard. I loved this combo!🔥
Choreo: @markmeismer ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Everleigh Rose on July 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, child and standing.

node.text: New headshot from the best week ever❤️ Thank you @ceventpics! & thank you @velocitydanceconvention for an incredible week of dancing and learning! At Velocity nationals I was thrilled to receive a platinum & 2nd overall for my contemporary solo “Heartbeat” by @thealexalba❤️ & also thrilled to get in the top 3 mini MVA with my “The Realest” solo by @autumnmiller! My duo “Blow” by @jblzk_ @thealexalba @savannaclairee got platinum 1st overall & “Legs” by @brynnebecker got Platinum 1st overall mini small group AND won the national mvp award! My two other groups “The List” and “Swine” by the amazing @thealexalba both got platinum & 3rd overall 🙌🏻 This has been the best season ever.. and I owe it all to my coaches and my amazing studio @paveschoolofthearts 🙌🏻 Sad to say bye to all of my amazing routines.. but ready for a brand new year!❤️

node.text: Had the best weekend ever at @radixdance 🙌🏻 I was honored to receive the core performer winner scholarship at convention and a “On The Edge” award and 3rd overall age 8-10 for my solo! Thank you @autumnmiller for this solo that I love so much! Also so excited to have received 1st overall for my duo & congrats to my team and coach @alexalba for our 1st overall, best of radix award for our group “Swine”! Thank you @paveschoolofthearts and all my teachers for pushing me to work hard and be the best I can be! I love my studio so much❤️🙌🏻

node.text:
I had so much fun with my dance family this past weekend competing and taking amazing dance classes from the talented teachers at @velocitydanceconvention! I’m so very thankful for my MVA scholarship and I’m honored that Velocity chose me as the MVA winner in the mini room.  I’m also so grateful to have received a diamond & first overall for my solo choreographed by @thealexalba 🙌🏻 I can’t wait to dance in the nationals finale show (choreographed by @wbezz) with my talented, fun Pave friends who also received scholarships.  Congrats  friends!  @paveschoolofthearts
Song: Rescue by @lauren_daigle

node.text: Feels GOOD to be back on stage✨ My first time doing a contemporary solo & I think I found what I truly LOVE! Thrilled to have received 5th overall out of almost 100 mini solos ages 10 and under and a “Stop The Clock” award & also a Non Stop Dancer award at @24sevendance! Most of all.. I had the best time & can’t wait to get back on stage again💛 Thanks to my teacher @thealexalba for this amazing solo & my studio @paveschoolofthearts and my girl @autumnmiller for always pushing me to be my best👏🏻 Link in bio for the full routine!
